OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776150320
OL,3,CMan trapped by tide in Sussex reunited
OL,4,Cwith RNLI crew that saved his life
OL,6,FA walker who was trapped by the rising
OL,7,Fwater below cliffs in Sussex has been
OL,8,Freunited with the lifeboat crew that
OL,9,Fsaved his life.
OL,11,FChris Haffenden thought he'd given
OL,12,Fhimself plenty of time for his walk
OL,13,Ffrom Seven Sisters to Birling Gap.
OL,15,FThe beaches below the Seven Sisters
OL,16,Fcliffs are frequently visited by
OL,17,Fwalkers and all too frequently visited
OL,18,Fby lifeboats.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
