PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776150320
OL,3,CMan trapped by tide in Sussex reunited
OL,4,Cwith RNLI crew that saved his life
OL,6,FChris Haffenden was reunited today
OL,7,Fwith the crew who saved him, after he
OL,8,Fwas trapped up in dangerously cold,
OL,9,Frough seas and cut off by a fast
OL,10,FSpring tide.
OL,12,FThe rescue was not straightforward due
OL,13,Fto challenging shore-dump conditions,
OL,14,Fwhich saw 1.5`2m waves breaking onto
OL,15,Fthe shore.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776150320
OL,3,CMan trapped by tide in Sussex reunited
OL,4,Cwith RNLI crew that saved his life
OL,6,FThe crew brought the inshore lifeboat
OL,7,Finto the shallows and one crew member
OL,8,Ffitted the casualty with a survivor
OL,9,Flifejacket, while the other two turned
OL,10,Fthe boat around manually and attempted
OL,11,Fto hold it in position in the powerful
OL,12,Fwaves.
OL,14,FAt times, the boat was lifted and
OL,15,Fturned by breaking waves, requiring
OL,16,Fsignificant skill and effort from the
OL,17,Fcrew to prevent it capsizing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776150320
OL,3,CMan trapped by tide in Sussex reunited
OL,4,Cwith RNLI crew that saved his life
OL,6,FAs the boat began taking on water and
OL,7,Fconditions made it difficult to
OL,8,Fmaintain position close to the shore,
OL,9,Fthe helm made the decision to withdraw
OL,10,Fbriefly from the breaking waves with
OL,11,Fthe casualty and two crew members on
OL,12,Fboard, allowing the lifeboat to be
OL,13,Fbailed out.
OL,15,FChris Haffenden, 44, who was rescued,
OL,16,Fsaid: "I set off for a walk from Seven
OL,17,FSisters Country Park and went down
OL,18,Fonto Birling Gap beach.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776150320
OL,3,CMan trapped by tide in Sussex reunited
OL,4,Cwith RNLI crew that saved his life
OL,6,F"But when I reached the cliffs to turn
OL,7,Faround, I realised the tide had come
OL,8,Fin almost instantly and I was stranded
OL,9,Fat the side of the cliff on a small
OL,10,Fsection of beach. It was mad how
OL,11,Fquickly the sea came in.
OL,13,F"I had no reception on my phone, just
OL,14,Fan old ham radio that I keep in the
OL,15,Fbottom of my bag, which can transmit
OL,16,Fon the marine channel. I got through
OL,17,Fto someone, but they told me to keep
OL,18,Ftrying to call 999 and eventually my
OL,19,Fcall went through.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776150320
OL,3,CMan trapped by tide in Sussex reunited
OL,4,Cwith RNLI crew that saved his life
OL,6,F"I've complained about people getting
OL,7,Fstuck here in the past but now it's
OL,8,Fhappened to me.
OL,10,F"The waves were powerful and
OL,11,Fdangerous, and the weather was
OL,12,Fmiserable, so there was no one around.
OL,13,FI was definitely panicking. But I felt
OL,14,Fa lot of relief when the lifeboat came
OL,15,Finto view."
OL,17,FDan Wittenberg, Volunteer lifeboat
OL,18,Fcrew member and D class Helm, said:
OL,19,F"This was a challenging rescue due to
OL,20,Fthe powerful shore-dump conditions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776150320
OL,3,CMan trapped by tide in Sussex reunited
OL,4,Cwith RNLI crew that saved his life
OL,6,F"The crew acted quickly to move the
OL,7,Fcasualty clear of immediate danger and
OL,8,Fmaintained constant communication and
OL,9,Fsupport throughout. Thankfully, we
OL,10,Fsafely recovered our third crew member
OL,11,Fbefore returning to the lifeboat
OL,12,Fstation with everybody safely on
OL,13,Fboard."
OL,15,FNo phone signal meant he couldn't call
OL,16,F999 but eventually a text made it
OL,17,Fthrough to the coastguard.
OL,19,FChris told his story today as the RNLI
OL,20,Flaunched its annual Mayday Mile fund-
OL,21,Fraising campaign.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
