OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776150320
OL,3,CMan trapped by tide in Sussex reunited
OL,4,Cwith RNLI crew that saved his life
OL,6,FHis rescue was one of 9000 callouts
OL,7,Facross the UK in one of the RNLI's
OL,8,Fbusiest years.
OL,10,FHis was one of 272 lives saved.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
